THIS HOME HAS LAMINATE FLO0RING IN LIVING ROOM, DINING ARE AND MASTER BDRM, WITH TILE FLOORING THROUGHOUT THE REST OF THE HOME FOR EASY CARE AND MAINTANANCE. AS YOU ENTER THE HOME THERE IS A LARGE LIVING ROOM W/ BAY WINDOW AND OFF OF LIVING ROOM IS A FORMAL DINING AREA WHICH LEADS TO A LARGE FLORIDA ROOM. THE KITCHEN HAS NEWER APPLIANCES AND LOVELY WOOD CABINETS, AND A BREAKFAST BAR, WHICH OPENS TO A FAMILY ROOM TO RELAX AND/OR ENTERTAIN IN. THE BDRMS ARE A SPLIT PLAN.
